    <description>&lt;p&gt;Attention English teachers living in Saigon: My friend has an English center on Tu Xuong Street in District 3 and is in urgent need of a substitute English teacher, and more permanent staff for the future. Please read the following then either call 848. 39326594 or &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.saigonist.com/node/add/teacher&quot;&gt;Create a Teacher Listing&lt;/a&gt; to be notified about other open English (or Vietnamese) teaching or tutoring jobs around Vietnam:&lt;/p&gt;
